WEBVTT

00:05.770 --> 00:08.020
我们都因彼此而经受过苦难
We have suffered at each other's hands.

00:08.690 --> 00:11.400
也因互相争斗而失去挚爱
We have lost people we love at each other's hands.

00:14.270 --> 00:16.060
这不是贵族与贵族间的战争
This isn't about noble houses,

00:16.440 --> 00:18.730
这是活人和死人的战争
this is about the living and the dead.

00:18.810 --> 00:20.440
而我打算待在活人中间
And I intend to stay amongst the living.

00:20.830 --> 00:23.700
<b>《权力的游戏》</b>

00:20.830 --> 00:23.700
<b>前情回顾</b>

00:22.190 --> 00:23.810
我给你个选择的机会
I offer you a choice.

00:24.020 --> 00:25.520
屈膝称臣 为我效力
Bend the knee and join me,

00:25.810 --> 00:27.730
或者拒不从命 死路一条
or refuse, and die.

00:32.020 --> 00:34.270
她来到维斯特洛是为了夺回七大王国
She is here to reclaim the Seven Kingdoms.

00:34.480 --> 00:36.440
而北境正是七国之一
The North is one of those seven kingdoms.

00:38.520 --> 00:41.270
夜王的大军一天天壮大起来
The Night King's army grows larger by the day.

00:45.230 --> 00:47.480
我们需要盟友 强大的盟友
We need allies. Powerful allies.

00:53.610 --> 00:54.980
这些怪物的确存在
The monsters are real.

00:56.270 --> 00:59.110
龙 异鬼 多斯拉克哮吼武士……
Dragons, White Walkers, Dothraki screamers...

01:00.360 --> 01:01.650
就让这些怪物自相残杀吧
Let the monsters kill each other.

01:02.020 --> 01:03.860
剩下的残局就留给我们来收拾
We will deal with whatever is left.

01:07.270 --> 01:09.060
我们将同心协力
We are going to destroy the Night King

01:09.150 --> 01:11.110
消灭夜王和他的军队
and his army, and we'll do it together.

01:12.650 --> 01:15.310
他宣誓为丹妮莉丝·坦格利安而战
He pledged to fight for Daenerys Targaryen.

01:15.610 --> 01:16.610
他已经屈膝称臣了
He's bent the knee.

01:17.060 --> 01:18.770
他需要知道真相
He needs to know the truth.

01:21.480 --> 01:23.190
琼恩不是我父亲的亲生儿子
Jon isn't really my father's son.

01:23.770 --> 01:25.650
他是雷加·坦格利安
He's the son of Rhaegar Targaryen,

01:25.860 --> 01:27.480
和我姑妈莱安娜·史塔克之子
and my aunt, Lyanna Stark.

01:28.650 --> 01:30.360
他是铁王座的继承人
He's the heir to the Iron Throne.

01:30.940 --> 01:32.310
我们要告诉他
We need to tell him.

01:37.440 --> 01:39.940
同样的事情也会发生在我们身上……
The same thing is coming for all of us...

01:42.980 --> 01:44.020
迫在眉睫
And it is here.

