<b>乔拉·莫尔蒙
</b>“大熊”


08:58.300 --> 09:00.350
<b>戴佛斯·席渥斯
</b>“洋葱骑士”


08:59.440 --> 09:02.310
- 艾莉亚呢？- 不知道躲哪去了
-Where's Arya? -Lurking somewhere.

09:08.940 --> 09:11.400
这是坦格利安家族的丹妮莉丝女王
Queen Daenerys of House Targaryen.

09:12.690 --> 09:16.520
这是我的妹妹 临冬城公爵夫人 珊莎·史塔克
My sister, Sansa Stark, the Lady of Winterfell.

09:16.610 --> 09:19.560
史塔克夫人 感谢你邀请我们来到你家
Thank you for inviting us into your home, Lady Stark.

09:19.650 --> 09:21.020
北境正如你哥哥所描绘的那样美丽
The North is as beautiful

09:21.110 --> 09:24.440
你也如北境的风光一样美丽动人
as your brother claimed, as are you.

09:27.940 --> 09:30.310
临冬城效忠于您 陛下
Winterfell is yours, Your Grace.

09:31.770 --> 09:33.610
我们现在没有时间聊这些
We don't have time for all this.

09:33.690 --> 09:37.480
夜王已经转化了您的龙 它成了尸鬼
The Night King has your dragon. He's one of them now.

09:38.480 --> 09:39.940
长城已破
The Wall has fallen,

09:40.020 --> 09:42.190
亡者大军正向南行进
the dead march south.

09:47.480 --> 09:49.400
一听到长城倒塌的消息
As soon as we heard about the Wall,

09:49.480 --> 09:52.610
我就召集了所有的封臣 撤退到临冬城
I called all our banners to retreat to Winterfell.

09:53.860 --> 09:54.860
安柏大人……
Lord Umber...

09:56.190 --> 09:59.150
你的人什么时候到？
when can we expect your people to arrive?

10:00.910 --> 10:03.330
<b>奈德·安柏
</b>最后壁炉城伯爵

10:03.360 --> 10:07.310
我们需要更多的马匹和马车 希望夫人允许
We need more horses and wagons, if it please my lady.

10:09.650 --> 10:11.270
以及大人……
And my lord.

10:13.610 --> 10:17.110
和女王陛下允许 抱歉
And my queen. Sorry.

10:17.190 --> 10:19.150
我们将为你倾囊相助
You'll have as many as we can spare.

10:19.230 --> 10:22.440
尽快回到最后壁炉城 带你的人过来
Hurry back to Last Hearth and bring your people here.

10:25.360 --> 10:28.150
我们还需要放出渡鸦 把消息传给守夜人
We need to send ravens to the Night's Watch as well.

10:28.230 --> 10:30.690
现在还在这些城堡驻扎已经毫无意义了
There's no sense in manning the castles anymore.

10:30.770 --> 10:31.860
我们要守住这里
We make our stand here.

10:31.940 --> 10:33.020
马上去办 陛下
At once, Your Grace.

10:34.020 --> 10:35.560
“陛下”
"Your Grace."

10:38.400 --> 10:41.410
<b>莱安娜·莫尔蒙
</b>熊岛伯爵夫人

10:41.190 --> 10:43.060
现在您已经不是陛下了 对吧？
But you're not. Are you?

10:44.020 --> 10:45.520
您离开临冬城的时候还是北境之王
You left Winterfell a king

10:45.610 --> 10:47.020
可回来时候却是一位——
and came back a--

10:49.520 --> 10:51.480
我不太清楚您现在的身份到底算什么
I'm not sure what you are now.

10:51.560 --> 10:54.110
公爵大人？
A lord?

10:54.190 --> 10:56.480
或者您现在什么都不是？
Nothing at all?

10:56.560 --> 10:58.770
- 这不重要 - 不重要？
-It's not important. -Not important?

10:59.940 --> 11:02.150
曾经 我们可是拥立您为北境之王
We named you King in the North.

11:03.730 --> 11:05.230
北境之王呐！
King of the North!

11:10.360 --> 11:12.110
确实 夫人
You did, my lady.

11:13.650 --> 11:15.480
那曾经是我人生中的荣光
It was the honor of my life.

11:15.560 --> 11:18.270
我将永远对你们的信任感念于心
I'll always be grateful for your faith.

11:20.400 --> 11:21.650
但当初我离开临冬城的时候
But when I left Winterfell,

11:21.730 --> 11:24.400
我告诉过大家我们需要盟友 否则我们只有死路一条
I told you we need allies or we will die.

11:25.560 --> 11:27.270
而现在我把盟友带回了家
I have brought those allies home

11:27.360 --> 11:29.440
与我们并肩作战
to fight alongside us.

11:30.730 --> 11:32.400
我必须做出选择
I had a choice,

11:32.480 --> 11:36.520
是保住我的王位还是保住北境
keep my crown or protect the North.

11:36.610 --> 11:38.480
我选择了北境
I chose the North.

11:50.860 --> 11:53.190
我们当中 要是有人能在接下来这场大战中活下来
If anyone survives the war to come,

11:53.270 --> 11:54.940
那就得感谢琼恩·雪诺
we'll have Jon Snow to thank.

11:56.400 --> 11:58.860
他冒着生命危险 证明威胁我们的东西是真实存在的
He risked his life to show us the threat is real.

11:58.940 --> 12:00.730
多亏了他的勇气
Thanks to his courage,

12:00.810 --> 12:02.860
我们才能带来
we have brought with us the greatest army

12:02.940 --> 12:04.020
有史以来最强大的军队
the world has ever seen.

12:04.110 --> 12:07.310
我们才能带回两条成年巨龙
We have brought two full-grown dragons.

12:09.480 --> 12:10.860
很快 兰尼斯特家族的军队
And soon, the Lannister army

12:10.940 --> 12:13.020
就会行军北上加入我们
will ride north to join our cause.

12:17.650 --> 12:19.150
我知道 我知道 我们家族
I know, I know, our people

12:19.230 --> 12:21.810
一直也算不上北境的盟友
haven't been friends in the past.

12:24.150 --> 12:25.860
但我们现在必须携手作战……
But we must fight together now...

12:26.980 --> 12:27.980
否则我们都会死
or die.

12:30.020 --> 12:32.480
我想问一下 我们该怎么供给
May I ask,how are we meant to feed

12:32.560 --> 12:34.520
这支有史以来最强大的军队呢？
the greatest army the world has ever seen?

12:34.610 --> 12:37.230
我能确保我们的存粮能撑过这个冬天
While I ensured our stores would last through winter,

12:37.310 --> 12:39.060
但我可没有料到还要给多斯拉克大军
I didn't account for Dothraki,

12:39.150 --> 12:42.860
无垢者 甚至两条成年巨龙做准备
Unsullied and two full-grown dragons.

12:44.480 --> 12:46.480
对了 龙吃什么？
What do dragons eat, anyway?

12:48.650 --> 12:49.980
想吃什么就吃什么
Whatever they want.

13:08.440 --> 13:12.270
嘿 注意点 小子 一丁点儿也不能漏掉
Hey, careful, lads.We need every last bit of it.

13:12.360 --> 13:13.650
抱歉
Sorry 'bout that.

13:17.860 --> 13:19.480
这是最后一车了吗？
Are these the last of the wagons?

13:19.560 --> 13:20.980
是的
Aye.

13:21.060 --> 13:23.690
好吧 全都推去锻造处
All right, let's get it all to the forges.

13:31.690 --> 13:32.690
大人
My lord.

13:33.290 --> 13:37.370
<b>约恩·罗伊斯
</b>“青铜约恩” 谷地领主

13:34.860 --> 13:35.860
夫人
My lady.

13:42.480 --> 13:43.520
我先退下了
My lady.

13:55.520 --> 13:56.940
临冬城公爵夫人
The Lady of Winterfell.

13:58.770 --> 14:00.730
这头衔不错啊
Has a nice ring to it.

14:00.810 --> 14:02.690
女王之手也不错
So does Hand of the Queen.

14:03.980 --> 14:06.020
这得看是哪位女王了
Depending on the queen, I suppose.

14:08.730 --> 14:11.440
我们上次谈话 还是在乔佛里的婚礼上
Last time we spoke was at Joffrey's wedding.

14:12.730 --> 14:15.520
- 真是不幸 - 总归有它的意义
- Miserable affair.- It had its moments.

14:21.230 --> 14:23.520
我很抱歉就那样离开了
Apologies for leaving like that.

14:23.610 --> 14:25.150
的确 有点难以解释
Yes,it was a bit hard to explain

14:25.230 --> 14:27.980
为什么在国王被谋杀后 我的妻子就逃跑了
why my wife fled moments after the king's murder.

14:30.560 --> 14:31.770
但我们现在都还活着
We both survived.

14:34.730 --> 14:36.440
许多人低估了你
Many underestimated you.

14:37.690 --> 14:39.270
他们当中 大部分都已经死了
Most of them are dead now.

14:47.230 --> 14:48.940
听到兰尼斯特大军北上的消息
I'm sure you weren't thrilled to hear

14:49.020 --> 14:50.900
你应该并不高兴吧
the Lannister army's marching north.

14:53.060 --> 14:56.190
你对我姐姐的恐惧可以理解
You have every right to be fearful of my sister.

14:56.270 --> 14:57.730
没人比我更怕她
No one fears her more than I do.

14:57.810 --> 15:00.730
- 但我一定会确保你的安全—— - 瑟曦跟你说
- But I promise, you'll be safe---Cersei told you her army

15:00.810 --> 15:03.560
她的军队会来北境为你作战？
was coming north to fight for you?

15:03.650 --> 15:04.650
是的
She did.

15:06.270 --> 15:07.690
你也信了？
And you believed her?

15:09.110 --> 15:10.810
她现在有了活下去的动力
She has something to live for now.

15:10.900 --> 15:13.690
我相信她是想活着的
I believe she wants to survive.

15:16.150 --> 15:18.650
我还以为你是世界上最聪明的人
I used to think you were the cleverest man alive.

15:50.650 --> 15:52.310
你以前看起来更高一些
You used to be taller.

15:55.110 --> 15:56.650
你怎么跟到我的？
How did you sneak up on me?

15:56.730 --> 15:59.560
你不是被一剑穿心了吗 你是怎么活下来的？
How did you survive a knife through the heart?

15:59.650 --> 16:01.150
其实我当时已经死了
I didn't.

16:19.480 --> 16:20.730
你还留着它
You still have it.

16:23.940 --> 16:25.150
缝衣针
Needle.

16:27.190 --> 16:29.060
你用过它吗？
Have you ever used it?

16:29.980 --> 16:31.730
一两次吧
Once or twice.

16:47.060 --> 16:48.900
瓦雷利亚钢剑
Valyrian steel.

16:50.480 --> 16:51.440
羡慕吗？
Jealous?

16:51.520 --> 16:54.690
对我来说太沉了
Too heavy for me.

17:02.860 --> 17:04.730
你之前去哪儿了？
Where were you before?

17:04.810 --> 17:07.520
你可以帮我跟珊莎说说好话的
I could've used your help with Sansa.

17:09.560 --> 17:11.770
她不喜欢你的女王 对吧？
She doesn't like your queen,does she?

17:11.860 --> 17:14.610
珊莎觉得她比谁都聪明
Sansa thinks she's smarter than everyone.

17:15.940 --> 17:17.980
她是我遇到过的最聪明的人
She's the smartest person I've ever met.

17:19.360 --> 17:20.650
你是在保护她吗？
Now you're defending her?

17:20.730 --> 17:22.110
是吗？
You?

17:23.440 --> 17:25.230
我保护的是我们的家族
I'm defending our family.

17:26.610 --> 17:27.770
她也一样
So is she.

17:27.860 --> 17:29.270
是啊
Yeah.

17:30.730 --> 17:32.310
我也是她的家人
I'm her family too.

17:38.360 --> 17:39.610
别忘了这一点
Don't forget that.

17:57.340 --> 18:00.470
<b>科本
</b>瑟曦的首相

17:57.440 --> 18:00.810
陛下 恐怕我带来了个坏消息
Your Grace, I'm afraid I bring terrible news.

17:59.340 --> 18:03.140
<b>瑟曦
</b>铁王座上的女王

18:01.980 --> 18:03.980
亡者大军已经攻破长城了
The dead have broken through the Wall.

18:07.610 --> 18:08.860
好
Good.

18:22.990 --> 18:25.830
<b>哈利·斯崔克兰
</b>黄金团团长

18:22.990 --> 18:25.830
<b>攸伦·葛雷乔伊
</b>铁群岛之王

18:42.100 --> 18:44.970
<b>亚拉·葛雷乔伊
</b>

18:43.060 --> 18:45.440
不如你就干脆一点杀了我吧
Why don't you just get it over with and kill me?

18:45.520 --> 18:48.480
我们可是一家人
But we're family.

18:49.690 --> 18:52.440
葛雷乔伊家族仅剩的几个
The last Greyjoys left in the world.

18:55.360 --> 18:57.610
或者说 仅剩的几个有种的
The last ones with balls anyway.

19:02.560 --> 19:03.900
我要是杀了你……
If I kill you...

19:05.360 --> 19:06.860
还跟谁说话去？
who can I talk to?

19:07.770 --> 19:09.150
嗯？
Hmm?

19:11.690 --> 19:14.020
我的船员都是哑巴
I've got a crew full of mutes.

19:17.360 --> 19:19.060
在海上 人就容易寂寞
It gets lonely at sea.

19:21.810 --> 19:23.730
我们这是到了君临？
Are we in King's Landing?

19:23.810 --> 19:24.900
嗯
Mm.

19:29.440 --> 19:31.560
你选错边了
You picked the losing side.

19:35.230 --> 19:37.900
那我就带着铁舰队去别处呗
Then I'll sail the Iron Fleet somewhere else.

19:44.980 --> 19:47.900
不过 我得先把女王操了
But first I'm gonna fuck the queen.

20:01.440 --> 20:03.190
两万人 是吗？
Twenty-thousand men, is it?

20:03.270 --> 20:06.310
是的 陛下 路上死了一些
Yes, Your Grace. A few died in transit.

20:08.610 --> 20:10.110
是因为他们玩骰子出老千
They cheated at dice.

20:12.060 --> 20:14.020
也许是我出老千
Or maybe I cheated.

20:14.110 --> 20:15.230
反正有人出了
Someone cheated.

20:17.310 --> 20:19.860
他们打仗不怎么厉害 没了也不是什么损失
They weren't good fighters. You won't miss them.

20:19.940 --> 20:21.860
- 马有多少？ - 两千匹
Horses? Two thousand.

20:21.940 --> 20:23.190
大象呢
And elephants?

20:23.270 --> 20:25.650
呃 禀告陛下 我们没有大象
Uh, no elephants, Your Grace.

20:27.270 --> 20:28.440
真让人失望
That's disappointing.

20:29.810 --> 20:31.980
我听说黄金团是有大象的
I was told the Golden Company had elephants.

20:32.060 --> 20:34.440
大象确实是非凡的猛兽 陛下
They are excellent beasts, Your Grace

20:34.520 --> 20:38.020
但不适应海上长途航行
but not well-suited to long sea voyages.

20:38.110 --> 20:39.650
不管怎样 君临都欢迎你们的到来
In any event, you are most welcome

20:39.730 --> 20:41.900
斯崔克兰团长
here in King's Landing, Captain Strickland.

20:41.980 --> 20:45.190
我们期待为您作战 陛下
We look forward to fighting on your behalf, Your Grace.

20:56.150 --> 20:57.810
那这里欢迎我吗
Am I most welcome here?

20:59.310 --> 21:01.940
你是王室真诚的朋友
You are a true friend of the crown

21:02.020 --> 21:03.900
也是备受尊敬的贵宾
and an honored guest.

21:03.980 --> 21:05.230
很好
Good.

21:05.310 --> 21:08.360
那作为真诚的朋友和尊敬的贵宾……
As a true friend and an honored guest...

21:12.700 --> 21:14.620
<b>格雷果·克里冈
</b>“魔山”

21:17.190 --> 21:20.360
我希望我们可以私下谈谈
I was hoping we could talk in private.

21:21.560 --> 21:23.770
战争结束再提此事 我们已经达成协议了
After the war. That was our agreement.

21:23.860 --> 21:27.690
战争也许会持续数年
Wars sometimes last years.

21:28.860 --> 21:31.360
你想要妓女 就去花金子买
You want a whore, buy one.

21:33.150 --> 21:34.520
你如果想要女王……
You want a queen...

21:35.810 --> 21:37.520
就得赢得她
earn her.

21:40.400 --> 21:41.360
我该怎么做？
How?

21:42.480 --> 21:43.810
我已经帮她主持正义
I've given her justice,

21:43.900 --> 21:46.610
给了她佣兵团和一支铁舰队
an army and the Iron Fleet,

21:46.690 --> 21:49.730
然而她却没有表露出一丝爱意
yet she gives me no sign of affection.

21:50.690 --> 21:52.860
我的心都要碎了
My heart is nearly broken.

21:55.150 --> 21:56.400
你太放肆了
You're insolent.

21:58.110 --> 22:02.520
- 因为无礼而被我处死的人 他们还没有你嚣张 - 他们在其他方面也不如我
-I've executed men for less. -They were lesser men.

22:41.310 --> 22:44.230
听说 龙烧死了一千个兰尼斯特士兵
I hear the dragon burnt up a thousand Lannister men.

22:43.590 --> 22:46.090
<b>波隆</b>

22:44.310 --> 22:46.230
死了几个我最喜欢的小伙子
Burnt up some of my favorite boys.

22:46.310 --> 22:47.980
- 是阿奇吗？ - 还有威廉
-Archie, was it? -And William.

22:48.060 --> 22:51.060
- 那个又高又帅的威廉？- 对 就是他
-Tall handsome William? -Yeah, tall handsome William.

22:51.150 --> 22:53.810
听说他被烧剩的骨头渣 只够盛满一个酒杯
They said what's left of him could fit in a wine glass.

22:53.900 --> 22:57.360
我是你们见过的 唯一一个射过龙的人
I am the only man you ever met who shot a dragon.

22:57.440 --> 22:59.190
- 真的？- 差点把它杀死了
-Did you? -Nearly killed it.

22:59.270 --> 23:00.230
那你真英勇
That's brave.

23:10.560 --> 23:13.110
- 那个叫艾迪的小子……   - 那个红头发的？
-That boy Eddie...  -The ginger?

23:11.500 --> 23:14.500
<b>还记得上一季的 Ed Sheeran 吗？</b>

23:13.190 --> 23:16.360
就是他 回来时脸都烧没了
That's him. Came back with his face burnt right off.

23:16.440 --> 23:17.690
他现在没有眼皮了
He's got no eyelids now.

23:17.770 --> 23:19.400
没眼皮他怎么睡觉啊？
How does he sleep with no eyelids?

23:19.480 --> 23:21.980
好了 能不能别他妈聊龙的事了？
All right, can we stop talking about the fucking dragons now?

23:22.060 --> 23:23.940
黑水河的波隆骑士
Ser Bronn of the Blackwater.

23:26.150 --> 23:27.230
你逗我呢吧
You're kidding me.

23:27.310 --> 23:28.730
抱歉打扰了
Apologies for the interruption,

23:28.810 --> 23:31.150
但女王确实催促我尽快前来
but the queen did urge me to hurry.

23:33.560 --> 23:34.770
抱歉 姑娘们
Sorry, ladies.

23:36.810 --> 23:38.360
下次吧
Another time perhaps.

23:46.060 --> 23:49.810
你有过空虚寂寞的时候吗 我挺喜欢年纪大的男人
You ever get lonely, I am partial to older gentlemen.

23:52.860 --> 23:56.110
可怜的姑娘 看这梅毒病情 她活不过一年了
Poor girl. The pox will take her within the year.

23:57.730 --> 23:59.730
- 你说哪个姑娘？ - 女王的弟弟们曾对你许诺
-Which girl? -The queen's brothers

23:59.810 --> 24:02.440
但他们没能坚守诺言
made promises to you and broke them.

24:02.520 --> 24:04.810
女王陛下想要弥补这个过失
Her Grace wants to rectify their mistake.

24:06.520 --> 24:08.940
她曾给了我城堡和妻子
She once gave me a castle and a wife,

24:09.020 --> 24:10.690
然后又全部从我手中夺走
then rectified me right out of them.

24:10.770 --> 24:13.060
那是詹姆爵士所为 与她无关
That was Ser Jaime's doing, not hers.

24:13.150 --> 24:15.020
如果瑟曦女王对你有所求
When Queen Cersei wants something,

24:15.110 --> 24:16.900
她会预付你黄金
she pays in advance and in gold.

24:16.980 --> 24:18.730
实际上 是成箱的黄金
Several chests of it, in fact.

24:18.810 --> 24:22.020
它们正在门外的马车里等着你
Waiting for you in a wagon just outside.

24:26.610 --> 24:31.440
所以她想杀人 又不能派自己的士兵去
So she wants to murder someone, but she can't send her soldiers.

24:31.520 --> 24:33.610
如果她盯上的的是龙女王……
If it's the Dragon Queen she's after...

24:33.690 --> 24:35.770
对于那个坦格利安女孩 她另有谋划
She has other plans for the Targaryen girl.

24:35.860 --> 24:37.940
啊 好吧 那祝计划成功
Yeah, well, good luck with that.

24:38.020 --> 24:39.860
女王的弟弟们可能不会
Our queen's brothers are unlikely

24:39.940 --> 24:42.270
在北境历险后平安归来
to survive their Northern adventures.

24:42.360 --> 24:44.690
但 万一他们活下来了……
But in the event that they do...

24:51.230 --> 24:54.900
陛下一向赏罚分明
She has a keen sense of poetic justice.

24:56.150 --> 24:57.980
这一家人都有病
That fucking family.

24:58.060 --> 24:59.810
学城驱逐我的时候
When the Citadel expelled me,

24:59.900 --> 25:01.730
我以为我会潦倒孤独而死
I thought I would die poor and alone,

25:01.810 --> 25:05.810
但为了回报我的衷心侍奉  瑟曦女王封我为女王之手
but in exchange for my service, Queen Cersei made me her Hand.

25:05.900 --> 25:07.770
如果有人能帮她除掉叛国的弟弟们
What would she do for the man

25:07.860 --> 25:10.230
她又会如何回报呢？
who rids her of her treasonous brothers?

25:26.360 --> 25:28.730
我本来想要大象的
I wanted those elephants.

25:34.810 --> 25:35.770
那……
So...

25:37.610 --> 25:41.610
我和那个胖国王比起来怎么样？
how do I compare to the fat king?

25:42.610 --> 25:44.440
你在侮辱我的先夫吗？
You're insulting my late husband?

25:44.520 --> 25:45.770
那你被冒犯了吗？
Are you offended?

25:50.360 --> 25:53.020
劳勃每晚都和不同的妓女过夜
Robert had a different whore every night

25:53.110 --> 25:56.110
但还是不懂该怎样对待女人的身体
but he still didn't know his way around a woman's body.

25:57.060 --> 25:58.150
跟弑君者比呢？
And the Kingslayer?

26:03.730 --> 26:05.770
你真是喜欢作死啊
You enjoy risking your neck, don't you?

26:07.440 --> 26:08.610
活着没意思
Life is boring.

26:08.690 --> 26:11.810
但你还有点意思 这一点我承认
You're not boring, I'll give you that.

26:23.810 --> 26:25.770
我是否取悦了女王陛下？
Do I please the queen?

26:27.230 --> 26:30.610
你可能是我遇见的最傲慢无礼的人
You might be the most arrogant man I've ever met.

26:32.770 --> 26:34.150
我喜欢
I like that.

26:36.020 --> 26:38.480
但现在我想独自待着
But now I want to be alone.

26:44.940 --> 26:47.770
我要让你怀上我的王子
I'm going to put a prince in your belly.

27:38.340 --> 27:40.300
<b>席恩·葛雷乔伊
</b>

28:22.060 --> 28:24.690
攸伦保不住铁群岛
Euron can't defend the Iron Islands,

28:24.770 --> 28:28.270
现在他和全部人马 舰队都在君临
not if he's in King's Landing with all his men and his ships.

28:29.400 --> 28:31.020
我们可以趁机夺回铁群岛
We can take our home back.

28:31.110 --> 28:32.610
丹妮莉丝去了北境
Daenerys went north.

28:32.690 --> 28:34.610
如果北境失守
Daenerys will need somewhere to retreat

28:34.690 --> 28:36.230
那丹妮莉丝就需要一条退路
if they can't hold the North.

28:36.310 --> 28:39.060
而尸鬼到不了铁群岛
Somewhere the dead can't go.

28:44.360 --> 28:47.610
我奉你为女王 听你号令 追随于你
You're my queen. I go where you command.

28:52.520 --> 28:54.520
你想去临冬城
You want to go to Winterfell.

28:54.610 --> 28:56.110
为史塔克家战斗
To fight for the Starks.

28:59.980 --> 29:00.980
去吧
Go.

29:05.770 --> 29:07.860
逝者不死
What is dead may never die.

29:11.360 --> 29:13.310
逝者不死
What is dead may never die.

29:18.020 --> 29:20.270
不管怎样 干掉那些杂种
But kill the bastards anyway.

29:48.060 --> 29:49.730
欢迎回家 小姐
Welcome back, my lady.

29:51.020 --> 29:52.440
请跟我来……
If you'd follow me...

29:52.520 --> 29:53.730
卡史塔克家来了
The Karstarks.

29:53.810 --> 29:55.980
他们的纹章不错
One of the better sigils.

29:57.150 --> 29:58.520
反正比洋葱好看
Beats an onion, anyway.

30:00.020 --> 30:01.610
无可辩驳
Can't argue with that.

30:01.690 --> 30:03.810
史塔克和卡史塔克在战场上互相残杀
Not so long ago, the Starks and the Karstarks

30:03.900 --> 30:06.270
才过去没多久
were slaughtering each other on the battlefield.

30:06.360 --> 30:08.360
是琼恩·雪诺让两家重归于好
Jon Snow brought peace to the houses.

30:08.440 --> 30:10.400
女王陛下对此感激不尽
And our queen is grateful.

30:10.480 --> 30:13.730
这自然很好 但重点不是这个
Her gratitude is lovely, but that's not my point.

30:13.810 --> 30:16.860
北境效忠于琼恩·雪诺 不是丹妮莉丝
The Northmen are loyal to Jon Snow, not to her.

30:16.940 --> 30:18.020
他们根本不认识她
They don't know her.

30:18.110 --> 30:20.440
自由民也不认她
The Free Folk don't know her.

30:20.520 --> 30:23.360
我在北境呆的时间不短 我跟你说
I've been up here a while, and I'm telling you,

30:23.440 --> 30:25.270
这儿的人倔得像牛
they're stubborn as goats.

30:25.360 --> 30:27.980
你得自己去争得他们的忠心
You want their loyalty, you have to earn it.

30:39.400 --> 30:41.900
你有什么好建议 说来听听
I sense that you're leading to a proposal.

30:43.060 --> 30:45.690
我的建议 就是联姻
A proposal is what I'm proposing.

30:45.770 --> 30:49.150
如果我们侥幸打败夜王 活了下来
On the off chance that we survive the Night King,

30:49.230 --> 30:50.770
如果七大王国能迎来
what if the Seven Kingdoms,

30:50.860 --> 30:53.270
史上他妈的第一次
for once in their whole shit history,

30:53.360 --> 30:56.900
由一位公正的女性和一位正直的男性共治的时代 会怎样呢？
were ruled by a just woman and an honorable man?

30:59.360 --> 31:01.190
他俩确实是天生一对
They do make a handsome couple.

31:01.270 --> 31:03.020
你高估我们的影响力了
You overestimate our influence.

31:03.110 --> 31:06.480
他们才不会听这些单身老男人的话
Jon and Daenerys don't want to listen to lonely old men.

31:06.560 --> 31:08.270
我可不是老男人
I'm not that old.

31:09.560 --> 31:10.980
没他那么老
Not as old as him.

31:12.770 --> 31:15.150
我们的女王很尊敬长者的智慧
Our queen respects the wisdom of age.

31:15.230 --> 31:16.610
当然
Of course she does.

31:16.690 --> 31:19.440
这就叫敬而远之
Respect is how the young keep us at a distance,

31:19.520 --> 31:23.020
好让我们不去忠言逆耳
so we don't remind them of an unpleasant truth.

31:23.110 --> 31:24.310
什么忠言
What is that?

31:25.440 --> 31:26.810
没有什么是永恒的
Nothing lasts.

31:28.360 --> 31:29.440
嘿！
Hey!

31:35.810 --> 31:38.270
你妹妹不喜欢我
Your sister doesn't like me.

31:42.810 --> 31:44.060
因为她不了解你
She doesn't know you.

31:45.980 --> 31:47.440
那我这样说你可能好受一些
If it makes you feel any better,

31:47.520 --> 31:49.270
小时候她也不喜欢我
she didn't like me either when we were growing up.

31:49.360 --> 31:51.480
我并不是要她把我当作朋友
She doesn't need to be my friend...

31:53.060 --> 31:54.980
但我是她的女王
but I am her queen.

31:58.480 --> 32:00.440
如果她不尊敬我……
If she can't respect me...

32:11.650 --> 32:13.500
今天它们吃了多少

32:13.600 --> 32:16.300
只有十八只山羊 十一只绵羊

32:19.310 --> 32:20.560
什么事
What's the matter?

32:20.650 --> 32:23.150
龙的胃口不太好
The dragons are barely eating.

32:37.140 --> 32:40.350
<b>雷哥
</b>丹妮莉丝的绿龙

32:40.520 --> 32:41.810
它们怎么了
What's wrong with them?

32:41.900 --> 32:43.480
它们不喜欢北境
They don't like the North.

32:59.730 --> 33:00.860
上来啊
Go on.

33:06.860 --> 33:09.310
我不会骑龙啊
I don't know how to ride a dragon.

33:09.400 --> 33:11.900
没人生来就会 骑上来就行了
Nobody does. Until they ride a dragon.

33:14.400 --> 33:15.900
要是它不想让我坐上去呢
What if he doesn't want me to?

33:15.980 --> 33:18.900
那我就会感谢你一直以来的陪伴 琼恩·雪诺
Then I've enjoyed your company, Jon Snow.

33:38.400 --> 33:40.020
该抓哪啊？
What do I hold onto?

33:41.480 --> 33:42.860
能抓什么抓什么吧
Whatever you can.

34:59.770 --> 35:00.690
啊！
Aah!

35:39.310 --> 35:41.650
你毁了我对骑马的兴趣
You've completely ruined horses for me.

35:50.730 --> 35:52.860
我们可以在这儿呆一千年
We could stay a thousand years...

35:55.020 --> 35:56.360
谁也找不到我们
no one would find us.

35:58.900 --> 36:00.230
到那时候 我们就很老了
We'd be pretty old.

36:08.400 --> 36:11.440
对南方姑娘来说 这里确实太冷了
It's cold up here for a southern girl.

36:11.520 --> 36:13.230
那还不给你的女王一点温暖
So keep your queen warm.

36:27.940 --> 36:29.060
别怕 没事儿
Don't be afraid.

36:42.610 --> 36:43.770
这个不错
That's good.

36:52.730 --> 36:54.480
- 詹德利？- 他在这儿
- Gendry? - He's here.

37:00.610 --> 37:03.480
用龙晶锻造这么大一把斧子可不容易
It isn't easy making a blade that big with dragonglass.

37:05.650 --> 37:07.940
你不是说自己很厉害吗 嗯？
You're saying you're good, is that it?

37:08.020 --> 37:10.020
我只是说 这材料挺棘手的——
I'm just saying it's a tricky material to--

37:10.110 --> 37:13.150
你知道给野人打造武器的都是什么人吗？
You know who makes weapons for the wildlings?

37:13.230 --> 37:15.610
不是瘸子就是混蛋
Cripples and cocksuckers.

37:15.690 --> 37:18.270
- 你是哪一类 - 放过他吧
- Which one are you? - Leave him be.

37:25.480 --> 37:27.060
我听说你来了
I heard you were here.

37:29.650 --> 37:31.110
你把我扔下等死
You left me to die.

37:32.150 --> 37:33.810
我还先抢劫了你呢
First I robbed you.

37:45.270 --> 37:47.610
你可真是个冷血小贱人啊
You're a cold little bitch, aren't you?

37:51.150 --> 37:53.360
看来你就是靠这一点才活到今天的
Guess that's why you're still alive.

38:01.060 --> 38:03.650
你为他打的那把斧子真不错
That was a nice ax you made for him.

38:03.730 --> 38:04.940
你比以前更厉害了
You've gotten better.

38:05.020 --> 38:07.480
哈 谢谢 你也一样
Yeah, thanks. So have you.

38:08.690 --> 38:11.020
我的意思是 你看起来不错
I mean, you look good.

38:12.520 --> 38:14.520
谢了 你也是
Thanks. So do you.

38:18.190 --> 38:21.020
要不是太冷 在这地方长大还挺不错的
It's not a bad place to grow up, if it wasn't so cold.

38:22.360 --> 38:24.060
那就靠炉子近一点儿
Stay close to that forge, then.

38:24.150 --> 38:27.770
- 这是命令吗？史塔克小姐 - 别这么叫我
- Is that a command, Lady Stark? - Don't call me that.

38:27.860 --> 38:30.020
遵命 小姐阁下
As you wish, milady.

38:37.310 --> 38:38.520
我想要这个
Here's my wish.

38:40.860 --> 38:41.980
你能做出来吗？
Can you make it?

38:42.060 --> 38:44.230
你用这东西做什么用？
What do you need something like this for?

38:44.310 --> 38:45.560
你到底能不能做出来？
Can you make it or not?

38:45.650 --> 38:48.520
你不是已经有一把剑了 这又是什么？
You already have a sword. What's that?

38:55.150 --> 38:56.480
这是瓦雷利亚钢
It's Valyrian steel.

38:56.560 --> 38:58.940
我就知道你也是个有钱姑娘
I always knew you were just another rich girl.

39:00.900 --> 39:03.440
说得好像你还认识其他有钱姑娘一样
You don't know any other rich girls.

39:13.940 --> 39:14.860
请进
Come in.

39:22.480 --> 39:24.230
葛洛佛大人祝我们好运
Lord Glover wishes us good fortune,

39:24.310 --> 39:27.650
但他会和手下人留在深林堡
but he's staying in Deepwood Motte with his men.

39:30.230 --> 39:32.480
“葛洛佛家族将继续效忠于史塔克家族
"House Glover will stand behind House Stark

39:32.560 --> 39:34.940
一如千年以来那样”
as we have for a thousand years."

39:36.110 --> 39:37.400
他之前不就是这么说的吗？
Isn't that what he said?

39:37.480 --> 39:40.400
他说的是 “我将效忠于琼恩·雪诺”
"I will stand behind Jon Snow," he said.

39:41.940 --> 39:43.270
“北境之王”
"The King in the North."

39:44.400 --> 39:46.150
我们需要盟友 我告诉过你
I told you we needed allies.

39:46.230 --> 39:49.480
可你没说过会放弃王位
You didn't tell me you were going to abandon your crown.

39:49.560 --> 39:51.690
我从没想过要当什么国王
I never wanted a crown.

39:51.770 --> 39:54.520
我只想要保护北境
All I wanted was to protect the North.

39:54.610 --> 39:57.360
我带回家两支军队 两条龙
I brought two armies home with me, two dragons.

39:57.440 --> 39:59.110
还有一位坦格利安家的女王
And a Targaryen queen.

39:59.190 --> 40:00.560
你真觉得
Do you think

40:00.650 --> 40:02.860
没有她 我们能打败尸鬼大军？
we can beat the Army of the Dead without her?

40:02.940 --> 40:05.900
珊莎 我亲自与它们战斗过 两次
I fought them, Sansa. Twice.

40:05.980 --> 40:08.190
如果你在意的是头衔称谓
You want to worry about who holds what title,

40:08.270 --> 40:10.730
那我就告诉你 这无关紧要
I'm telling you it doesn't matter.

40:10.810 --> 40:13.480
没有她 我们连一丝胜算都没有
Without her, we don't stand a chance.

40:22.400 --> 40:24.980
你相信我吗？哪怕一点儿
Do you have any faith in me at all?

40:26.560 --> 40:27.860
你懂我的 一如既往
You know I do.

40:32.310 --> 40:33.940
她会是一位优秀的女王
She'll be a good queen.

40:35.020 --> 40:36.110
对我们所有人而言
For all of us.

40:37.770 --> 40:39.270
她不像她的父亲那样
She's not her father.

40:45.810 --> 40:47.480
对 她可漂亮多了
No, she's much prettier.

40:52.980 --> 40:55.440
你屈膝下跪 究竟是为了拯救北境
Did you bend the knee to save the North

40:55.520 --> 40:57.020
还是因为你爱上了她？
or because you love her?

41:21.020 --> 41:22.310
噢！
Oh!

41:23.000 --> 41:25.250
<b>山姆威尔·塔利
</b>

41:25.730 --> 41:26.980
就是你吗？
So you're the man?

41:27.060 --> 41:28.520
呃
Um...

41:28.610 --> 41:30.650
女王陛下 您说的是？
Which man am I, Your Grace?

41:30.730 --> 41:33.980
无人能够挽救乔拉爵士的性命时 是你挺身而出
The one who saved Ser Jorah when no one else could.

41:34.060 --> 41:36.230
他们可以出手 只是不愿罢了
They could, they just wouldn't.

41:37.560 --> 41:39.480
当我夺回王位时
I'll have to make some changes

41:39.560 --> 41:41.310
会对学城进行一些调整
in the Citadel when I take my throne.

41:41.400 --> 41:43.980
你尽心竭力的服务配得上一流的回报
A great service merits a great reward.

41:44.060 --> 41:46.730
噢 能够为您服务就是我的荣幸了 陛下
Oh, it's my honor to serve you, Your Grace.

41:46.810 --> 41:49.860
很好 不过我总能赏赐给你一些东西吧
Well, there must be something I could give you.

41:51.230 --> 41:53.980
恕我冒昧
If it's not too much trouble,

41:54.060 --> 41:56.480
我想请求您的宽恕
I could use a pardon.

41:56.560 --> 41:57.810
你犯下了什么罪过呢？
For what crime?

41:57.900 --> 41:59.060
呃
Um--

41:59.150 --> 42:01.900
我从学城借走了一些书
I borrowed a few books from the Citadel.

42:04.270 --> 42:06.310
还有一把剑
And also a sword.

42:06.400 --> 42:08.860
- 剑也是学城的？- 不 剑属于我的家族
- From the Citadel? - From my family.

42:10.400 --> 42:12.270
那把剑是塔利家族的 代代相传
It's been in House Tarly for generations.

42:12.360 --> 42:15.440
最后本该传到我的手上
It would've been mine anyway, eventually,

42:15.520 --> 42:18.480
但我的父亲另有打算
but my father had other ideas.

42:20.860 --> 42:22.230
令尊不会是蓝道·塔利吧？
Not Randyll Tarly?

42:24.190 --> 42:25.610
您认识他？
You know him?

42:29.480 --> 42:32.190
若他那时向我屈膝投降
I offered to let him retain his lands and titles

42:32.270 --> 42:33.360
我会允许他保留封地和头衔
if he bent the knee.

42:36.440 --> 42:37.560
可他拒绝了
He refused.

42:47.270 --> 42:48.610
那
Well...

42:50.770 --> 42:52.690
既然如此 我弟弟就是角陵伯爵了
At least I'll be allowed home again,

42:52.770 --> 42:54.440
至少我还可以回家吧
now that my brother's the lord.

42:58.480 --> 43:00.940
他和令尊坚持同样的立场
Your brother stood with your father.

43:15.360 --> 43:16.480
嗯
Hm.

43:17.980 --> 43:19.900
陛下 谢谢您
Thank you, Your Grace.

43:19.980 --> 43:21.400
把这一切告诉我
For telling me.

43:21.480 --> 43:23.230
那我
And m--

43:23.310 --> 43:25.860
- 我可否…… - 退下吧
- May I...? - Of course.

44:08.650 --> 44:10.520
你在这里做什么？
What are you doing out here?

44:11.730 --> 44:14.020
等 等一个老朋友
Waiting, for an old friend.

44:15.360 --> 44:17.440
是时候告诉琼恩真相了
It's time to tell Jon the truth.

44:18.480 --> 44:20.480
不 我不行
No, no.

44:20.560 --> 44:24.440
你是他的弟弟 不该由你来告诉他吗
You're his brother.Shouldn't you tell him?

44:24.520 --> 44:26.650
我不是他的弟弟
I'm not his brother.

44:26.730 --> 44:29.020
他信任你胜过任何人
He trusts you more than anyone.

44:30.060 --> 44:32.060
现在是时候了
Now's the time.

45:07.150 --> 45:08.610
山姆？
Sam?

45:08.690 --> 45:12.480
抱歉 我知道我不应该下到这来
I'm sorry, I know I'm not supposed to be down here.

45:15.730 --> 45:18.110
- 你一直在躲着我吗？ - 当然不是
- Were you hiding from me? - Of course not.

45:19.270 --> 45:21.360
你怎么会在临冬城？
What are you doing in Winterfell?

45:21.440 --> 45:24.110
难道你已经读完了学城所有的书？
Or did you read every book in the Citadel already?

45:27.610 --> 45:29.310
怎么了？
What's wrong?

45:29.400 --> 45:30.860
吉莉？她没事吧？
Gilly? Is she all right?

45:30.940 --> 45:32.770
- 她没事 - 小山姆呢？
- She's good. - Little Sam?

45:34.900 --> 45:35.900
你不知道吗？
Don't you know?

45:37.270 --> 45:38.400
知道什么？
Know what?

45:39.810 --> 45:40.810
丹妮莉丝……
Daenerys...

45:41.980 --> 45:45.150
她处死了我父亲还有弟弟
she executed my father and brother.

45:45.230 --> 45:46.810
他们是她的俘虏
They were her prisoners.

45:50.770 --> 45:52.810
她没告诉你
She didn't tell you.

46:01.190 --> 46:02.480
对此我很遗憾
I'm so sorry.

46:05.980 --> 46:07.690
我们需要结束这场战争
We need to end this war.

46:09.440 --> 46:11.020
换做你 也会那么做吗？
Would you have done it?

46:13.110 --> 46:15.060
我也处死过不服从我的人
Well, I've executed men who disobeyed me.

46:15.150 --> 46:16.860
但你也宽恕过很多人
You've also spared men.

46:16.940 --> 46:19.520
几千拒绝屈膝臣服的野人
Thousands of wildlings when they refused to kneel.

46:19.610 --> 46:21.060
那时我又不是国王
I wasn't a king.

46:23.440 --> 46:24.480
不 你是
But you were.

46:26.190 --> 46:27.520
你一直都是
You've always been.

46:29.480 --> 46:31.190
我已经放弃王位了 山姆
I gave up my crown, Sam.

46:31.980 --> 46:32.980
我已屈膝臣服
I bent the knee.

46:33.060 --> 46:34.610
不再是北境之王了
I'm not King in the North anymore.

46:34.690 --> 46:36.270
我说的不是北境之王
I'm not talking about the King in the North.

46:36.360 --> 46:39.610
我说的是他妈整个七大王国的国王
I'm talking about the King of the bloody Seven Kingdoms.

46:47.190 --> 46:48.900
布兰和我查清楚了
Bran and I worked it out.

46:48.980 --> 46:51.810
我拿到一本总主教的日记 布兰有……
I had a High Septon's diary.Bran had...

46:52.940 --> 46:54.270
先不提布兰有什么了
whatever Bran has.

46:54.360 --> 46:56.310
你到底在说什么？
What are you talking about?

46:59.440 --> 47:00.480
你的母亲
Your mother...

47:01.650 --> 47:02.980
是莱安娜·史塔克
was Lyanna Stark.

47:04.560 --> 47:05.900
而你的父亲……
And your father...

47:07.190 --> 47:09.150
你的亲生父亲
your real father

47:09.230 --> 47:10.900
是雷加·坦格利安
was Rhaegar Targaryen.

47:13.060 --> 47:15.690
你从来都不是什么私生子
You've never been a bastard.

47:15.770 --> 47:19.520
你真名为伊耿·坦格利安 铁王座真正的继承人
You're Aegon Targaryen,true heir to the Iron Throne.

47:23.770 --> 47:26.560
抱歉 我知道这些很难接受
I'm sorry,I know it's a lot to take in.

47:35.770 --> 47:39.110
我父亲是我见过的最信守荣誉之人
My father was the most honorable man I ever met.

47:42.650 --> 47:44.730
你却告诉我他骗了我一辈子
You're saying he lied to me all my life.

47:44.810 --> 47:45.940
不
No.

47:46.940 --> 47:50.440
你父亲 好吧 奈德·史塔克
Your father-- Well, Ned Stark.

47:50.520 --> 47:53.900
他向你母亲承诺会一直保护你
He promised your mother he'd always protect you.

47:53.980 --> 47:56.770
而他确实做到了 劳勃如果知道了真相一定会杀了你
And he did. Robert would have murdered you if he knew.

47:58.770 --> 48:00.270
你才是真正的国王
You're the true king.

48:01.440 --> 48:03.310
伊耿·坦格利安六世
Aegon Targaryen,Sixth of His Name,

48:03.400 --> 48:05.400
全境守护者 还有那一串头衔
Protector of the Realm,all of it.

48:19.940 --> 48:22.900
- 丹妮莉丝是我们的女王 - 可她不该是
- Daenerys is our queen. - She shouldn't be.

48:24.810 --> 48:26.810
- 你这是叛国 - 我这是说出真相
- That's treason. - It's the truth.

48:28.560 --> 48:31.150
你能为保护子民而放弃王位
You gave up your crown to save your people.

48:32.810 --> 48:34.480
她也能做到吗？
Would she do the same?

48:53.860 --> 48:56.200
<b>托蒙德
</b>“巨人克星”

48:58.990 --> 49:02.250
<b>贝里·唐德利恩
</b>“闪电大王”

50:42.690 --> 50:44.360
退后 这家伙眼睛是蓝的！
Stay back, he's got blue eyes!

50:44.440 --> 50:46.060
我的眼睛一直是蓝的！
I've always had blue eyes!

50:49.000 --> 50:51.360
<b>艾迪森·托勒特
</b>“忧郁的艾迪” 守夜人指挥官

50:56.110 --> 50:57.270
你找到什么人了吗？
Did you find anyone?

51:30.650 --> 51:32.810
安柏家的男孩
The Umber boy.

51:32.900 --> 51:34.020
这是个讯息
It's a message.

51:35.150 --> 51:36.730
夜王留下的讯息
From the Night King.

51:36.810 --> 51:40.480
他的大军已经先我们一步去往临冬城了 而我们只能步行
His army's between us and Winterfell. We're on foot.

51:40.560 --> 51:42.400
我们是从黑城堡骑马来的
We rode down from Castle Black.

51:42.480 --> 51:44.730
咱们可以两人骑一匹马
We can double up on the horses.

51:44.810 --> 51:48.730
如果马能撑得住 我们可以赶在尸鬼大军之前抵达
If the horses last, we'll get there before the dead.

51:48.810 --> 51:49.940
只能说但愿
We just have to hope

51:50.020 --> 51:51.730
夜王不会先到一步
the Night King doesn't come first.

52:43.400 --> 52:45.940
走起来！往前走！
Keep moving! Straight up!

52:47.810 --> 52:50.730
跟上！别落后！
Stay together!Don't fall behind!

53:07.620 --> 53:10.910
<b>詹姆·兰尼斯特
</b>“弑君者”

53:44.610 --> 55:01.000
<b>衣柜字幕组出品</b>  

53:44.610 --> 55:01.000
